summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5108 for the improvement of the alley between Blocks 2 and 3, Supplemental Plat of Wild Rose Addition, and east of Block 2, Wild Rose Addition, being the alley between 8th Avenue West and 9th Avenue West, from West McGraw Street to West Wheeler Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same.
